n: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">不仅为新中国赢得了朋友</span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">也赢得了尊敬</span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">不仅扩大了新中国的国际影响</span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">更提高了新中国的国际地位和国际威望</span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">周总理和他率领的中国代表团在万隆的活动</span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">是新中国外交史上一座不朽的丰碑</strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">是他让所有人见证了新中国的有力</span></strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; min-height: 1em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 14px; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">是他让全世界认识到新中国的铿锵</span></strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 40px; max-inline-size: 100%; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">03.</span></strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">鞠躬尽瘁，为中国能有今日死而后已</span></strong></span></section><section style="margin: 24px 16px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 0em; text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-size-adjust: inherit; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 0em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">1972年5月</span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 0em; text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-size-adjust: inherit; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 0em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">74岁的周总理</span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 0em; text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-size-adjust: inherit; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 0em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">被确诊患膀胱癌</span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">自1974年6月1日住院<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">到1976年1月8日去世</span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">他共做大小手术13次</strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">约40天左右就要动一次手术</strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">即便遭受病痛折磨</span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">他仍旧超负荷工作</span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">每天起草和批阅文件<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); text-wrap: wrap; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 2em; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 122, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">连续工作12小时以上<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></span></strong></span></section><section style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 